      "content": "ive been having these crazy experiences lately... like everything in nature is trying to tell me something. yesterday i was walking in the park and every single bird in the trees just went silent at once when i passed by, and then today i found those weird geometric patterns in the frost on my window. it feels like there's a specific reason i'm seeing these things right now. do u think it's just coincidence or is there something deeper going on?",
